title: $:/plugins/oeyoews/tiddlywiki-fancybox
author: oeyoews
name: Tiddlywiki Fancybox
readme:
!! Readme

<!-- * 只需要安装此插件即可， 无需额外配置， 自动识别图片tiddlywiki当前界面(不是所有)的所有图片, -->
<!-- 点击即可放大图片(如果不起作用, 请刷新tiddlywiki使用)， -->
`Updated Time:  2023-01-09 20:02:49+0800`
 <!-- 后期更新说明请点击 [[readme|https://oeyoewl.top/fancybox-gallery-tiddlywiki]] -->

* [[Demo|https://neotw.netlify.app/main.html#%24%3A%2Fplugins%2Foeyoews%2Ftiddlywiki-fancybox]]

* [[Source|https://github.com/oeyoews/neotw/tree/main/dev/plugins/tiddlywiki-fancybox]]

* [[Tiddlyhost site|https://fancybox-oeyoews.tiddlyhost.com]]

!! Features

* support download images, fullscreen, custom style and shortcuts,
<!-- !! Note -->
<!-- * 由于是动态给img加上一个父标签, -->
<!-- 只会渲染启动时识别到的img标签，如果导入新的图片或者打开新的含有图片的tiddler, -->
<!-- 则需要重新刷新当前界面，让插件重新渲染DOM -->
<!-- * how to add refresh tip on tiddlywiki js?? -->

!! Usage

<!-- !!! 分组 -->
<!-- * 如果一个tiddler 中的图片来自多个其他的tiddler, 则会展示多个tid的图片分组, -->
<!-- 如果当前tiddler的图片全部来自单个tiddler则会只会展示一个图片分组(此功能目前借助<<qualify>> -->
<!-- 宏实现) -->
{{$:/plugins/oeyoews/tiddlywiki-fancybox/example}}

!! Links

* fancybox: https://github.com/fancyapps/fancybox

!! Note

* if you use splashscreen, please remove `remove-when-wiki-loaded` class,
otherwise this plugin will not work normally [[warn|https://github.com/Jermolene/TiddlyWiki5/search?q=tc-remove-when-wiki-loaded]]
* not support local svg at least

!! TODO

* use widget or js macro instead macro

title: $:/plugins/oeyoews/tiddlywiki-publish-tiddler
author: oeyoews
name: Tiddlywiki Publish Tiddler
readme:
* Publish Tiddler Manager
* not save storylist to html
* support Publish or not manager

!! NOTE

* 需要手动启用FileSystem 文件
* 此插件重写 [[FileSystem Tid|$:/config/FileSystemPaths]]
* 虽然此插件兼容单文件tiddlywiki, 但是只工作在nodejs tiddlywiki
* maybe should use public is more understandable better publish
* 在第一次启动时, 控制台可能会多出很多 `syncer-browser-tiddlyweb: Checking dirty status` 类似与这样的日志

title: $:/plugins/oeyoews/tiddlywiki-static-page
author: oeyoews
name: Tiddlywiki Static Page
readme:
此插件不建议普通tiddlywiki用户使用, 并且只适用于tiddlywiki nodejs版本,
!! Tips !! Tutorials 需要在tiddlywiki.info 文件中添加这样一段代码， 然后在命令行中运行 `(npx) tiddlywiki --build static` ```wikitext "static": [ "--output", "dist", "--rendertiddlers", "[!is[system]]", "$:/core/templates/static.tiddler.html", "static", "text/plain", "--rendertiddler", "$:/core/templates/static.template.css", "static/static.css", "text/plain" ] ``` * Tiddlywiki Static Page * [[Source|https://github.com/oeyoews/neotw/tree/main/dev/plugins/tiddlywiki-static-page]] * [[Demo|https://oeyoews.github.io/neotw/main]]
